storyInfo: Feist's group encounters Hoederer as they try to rescue their comrades inside the factory. W takes the rear guard to cover Amiya and the Self-Salvation Corps' retreat.

attributes.content: This way, through the smoke! Follow the light of the fire!
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Devil...!
attributes.name: Londinium Citizen

attributes.content: What's this? An egg mixer?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Did you think you could hurt a Sarkaz mercenary with a toy like this?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: S-Stay back!
attributes.name: Londinium Citizen

attributes.content: Calm down. Over here, behind me.
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: This one's on our side... for now.
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Your side? Better not be too sure of yourself on that one.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: W... it would be wise if you made an effort to be easier to work with. That is, if you hope to get any information out of me.
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: That's a pretty roundabout threat there...
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Say... you wouldn't happen to be Kal'tsit's illegitimate daughter, would you?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: What are you—
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Nah, you two look nothing alike. Plus, how could that icy old hag have any kids?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Screw it. No way I could ever get buddy buddy with a lady like you.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Suits me just fine.
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Don't you worry, I won't be here long. I know how much my head's worth in merc circles, and I'm not in a generous mood.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Alright, there.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Bombs... you buried more bombs. Did you blow up the other paths?
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Where are your men? Aren't they still fighting the Sarkaz in the plant?
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Do you really want to know?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Explaining the whole deal would be a huge pain. Let's skip right to the good part.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: They're all dead.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Dead?
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Did you think it would be easy to scoop you out of there? I lost most of the Londinium recruits I picked up the past few months in that nasty old factory.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: So this had better be worth it. Can we go now?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Let me do a head count...
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: Alright, everyone in the southern plant escaped.
attributes.name: Heidi

attributes.content: I was hired to snag you, not an entire congregation. Tell Kal'tsit I'm charging double for this mess.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Bring your hooded monster and let's—what are you standing around for?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: W, was it you who blew up this path?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Duh. Not about to give our pursuers any chances.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: But Feist and his team just left.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Oh, come on... getting lost like this, at your age?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: What's the situation, Blake?
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: They're down.
attributes.name: Victorian Soldier

attributes.content: Good. Keep moving.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Horn, to your left!
attributes.name: Victorian Soldier

attributes.content: Dublinn... I'll have your head!
attributes.name: Sarkaz Warrior

attributes.content: Not Dublinn here. Not that you'll get the chance to wallow in your disappointment.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Another? How many Sarkaz bodies have we seen?
attributes.name: Victorian Soldier

attributes.content: All Dublinn?
attributes.name: Victorian Soldier

attributes.content: Looks like it.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Horn, I don't know how to put this, but...
attributes.name: Victorian Soldier

attributes.content: Dublinn saved us a lot of effort.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: There's no shame in admitting it. How long have you been with me here in Sudean? We need to use every means at our disposal if we want to survive.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Come on, left door here.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Ready?
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Clear.
attributes.name: Victorian Soldier

attributes.content: Good. Now the right side.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Watch the corners, Robben. I don't want any surprises.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Roger.
attributes.name: Robben

attributes.content: Go!
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: *Cough* G-Go away, devil! We're not talking!
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: Found them.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Y-You're...
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: Friends.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: I never thought... we heard sounds of fighting, saw the flicker of Arts... I thought it was some new devil torture method.
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: Sorry we couldn't get here earlier.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Can you stand, soldier?
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Soldier... haven't heard that in a long time.
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: You an officer? You've got nerve to come here—
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: What are you doing? We're here to save you!
attributes.name: Robben

attributes.content: Save me? Why? So I can get tricked again? So I can die in your next plot with the foreigners?
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: In your dreams, 'sir'! We'd rather die here!
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: Very well.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Robben, your crossbow.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Horn? What are you—
attributes.name: Robben

attributes.content: Ammo is precious and not to be wasted.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: But these are compatriots, loyal soldiers of Victoria.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: If their last wish is to die here, then we'll grant it.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: You'll really kill me?
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: You'll die as you wish in this dark room, forgotten by Londinium.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: You'll turn to bleached bones in this old abandoned factory, until the dust and dirt bury you.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Or, you could do something different with this crossbow.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: You could take it, come with us, and fight your way out.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Perhaps you'll still get your wish and die trying.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: But you'll have a chance to see the night sky, breathe the air full with the smell of rust and oil—
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: And think about your loved ones, breathing that same air.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: I swear on my life that they'll remember what you gave.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Yes... they... they could still be alive...
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: Have you made your choice? Time's flying.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: I'll go with you. Give me a weapon.
attributes.name: Prisoner

attributes.content: What about the others? Are you coming too?
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Good. Blake, you have seven... nine new men.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Tell me your names before we move out, soldiers.
attributes.name: Horn

attributes.content: Closure, have you made contact with the Self-Salvation Corps team?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Hold on... I just got this drone restarted... it's different from the other one...
attributes.name: Drone

attributes.content: This isn't good.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Heidi, lead the other civilians out of here. The 3rd regiment will be waiting—
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: W?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Hey, all the mines I left behind got blown up! Do you know what that means? Means a lotta guys are chasing us right now.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Using up my men wasn't enough for you, huh? You gotta use up my bombs too?
attributes.name: W

attributes.options: Five minutes.;We can't wait any longer.

attributes.content: Alright, five minutes it is.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Closure, get in touch with Feist and tell him that he and Rockrock need to be back within 5 minutes.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Doctor, we'll have to join the battle.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Bill, be honest with me... have you put on weight? You're heavier than I thought...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Hehe... how about this?
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Hey, that's better.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: What did you do? Some magic trick?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Ha, just a change of posture... *cough*
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: A-Alright, just stay put, don't open your wounds.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: When I saw you lying in that pool of blood, I thought...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Thought I was dead?
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Ha... those devils don't got the skills... it's just... ouch...
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Take a break, don't talk anymore.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Have you found an exit, Rockrock? The Sarkaz must have done something with these rooms... I feel like we're going around in circles.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: I heard the sound of fighting a few minutes ago.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: The exit should be around here...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Nrgh...
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Never mind what I just said, Bill. Keep talking so you don't fall asleep.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Remember the reward you asked for? After that last win?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Er... a fruit can?
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: A FRUIT CAN? You said you wanted a mechanical metal crab to give to your niece in the City!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Yeah, I was hungry... lucky you've got a good memory.
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Good memory? I didn't sleep at all the next few days, working on that thing between missions...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: You'd better hang in there after all the effort I put in!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: *Cough* Alright, boss... whatever you say.
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Footsteps!
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Oh no! Sarkaz—
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Where did they go?
attributes.name: Sarkaz Warrior

attributes.content: There's a blood trail. They can't have gone far.
attributes.name: Sarkaz Warrior

attributes.content: We should hurry.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Er...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Come on, Captain, I'll take the other side.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Sigh... look at me, can't even walk without two people helping me.
attributes.name: Bill

attributes.content: Don't say that. We're family, and we look out for each other.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Captain, they're catching up!
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: Hold them off, Johnny! Gabby, you've got the grenades, right? Give us some cover!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Roger!
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: Rockrock, has Rock-17 found a way out? We're counting on it!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Right-turn here!
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Alright, to the right!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Wait... who's talking? Rock-17? Y-You can talk?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: What's that, some dumb engineering joke?
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Took me ages to hack this drone's system... I didn't change anything, ok? The system was too simple.
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: ...Closure?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Yes, it's me. I didn't have a chance to install voice data onto your drone, so I have to synthesize it... not cute enough?
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Well... it actually sounds rather like you.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Where do we go from here?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Left-turn... wait, no, there are Sarkaz there. I mean enemy Sarkaz! Go back—
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: There are even more enemies to the rear.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Well then... let me think...
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Right, let's go upwards!
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Don't you have that flying gear? Er, I mean grappling hook! There's a vent above you that should allow a man to pass through...
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Should?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: We have wounded here. Gotta be sure.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Well... I'll need Rockrock to take control of the drone for a moment...
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Alright.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: What do we do?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Rockrock... do you really trust her?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Do you have a better plan?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Captain, they're coming! I can see their leader!
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: Quick, open the vent!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Gotcha! Rockrock, aim!
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Rock-17—
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Is it open?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Almost.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Again!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Rock...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: It missed! H-How did that sword...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Finally found a way out? Isn't it a little late?
I'll hold him off! Quick—
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: Blind courage isn't worth much in battle.
Johnny!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Rockrock, the vent!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: I... I can't...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: I've got two grenades left. Even the Sarkaz can't—
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: What the... the grenade got cut in half?!
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: Captain, this is no ordinary Sarkaz—
attributes.name: Self-Salvation Corps Soldier

attributes.content: Gabby!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: I'm just an ordinary mercenary.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Did you really think you could beat Manfred or Theresis?
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Pretty naive.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Sarkaz... did you think all I had was grenades?
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Grenades? Smoke bombs is more like it.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Bombs that can hurt a Sarkaz don't look like that.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Feist, Rockrock, you hear me? I've recalibrated... but you only have one chance. Hold on tight!
attributes.name: Rock-17

attributes.content: Rockrock—
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: It worked! We can go up now!
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: You first!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: No, you're with BIll, you go first—
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Alright.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: You're not getting through, Sarkaz!
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: I'll protect my family... you won't hurt them again!
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Rock-17!
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Self-destruct drone?
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Pathetic...
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Captain... go...
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Tell me, Feline... was it really worth it? Losing that many to save one?
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Every one of them called out for their captain with their last breaths.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Will you take responsibility for their sacrifice?
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: ...I would rather none of them died.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Hold on, Rockrock!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: The grappling hook again? Smart, but not smart enough.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: You need better tricks to survive in battle.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: We'll meet again, children... you don't know it, but there's no way you'll leave this inferno.
attributes.name: Hoederer

attributes.content: Are they here, Closure?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Four minutes, fifty seconds.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Countdown?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: We...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Amiya!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: They're here!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Feist? Just the three of you? The other two...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: They won't be back.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: We need to get out of here, now!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: There's a really dangerous Sarkaz after us, and there are a lot of them... it's an ambush!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: None of us would have made it, if not for Closure...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: They knew we'd go there, and they know you're here. They're just waiting... it's a trap! We have to go, before it's too late!
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: It's too late.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Damn it, this is my last mine, and the biggest one.
attributes.name: W

attributes.options: Another last one?;How many last ones is that?

attributes.content: Stop bothering me, {@nickname}. Yes, I have one bomb left. Guess who it's for?
attributes.name: W

attributes.options: Are you nervous?;Got your hands full?

attributes.content: You didn't notice the explosion sounded kinda weird? I guess there's really nothing under that tin head of yours.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: The guy didn't fall into my trap at all. He avoided it and disabled the Originium circuits.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Need me to say it even clearer? No, it didn't take me too much effort to set up the mines...
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: But the dragon lady was the last one to put all my mines out of commission.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Talulah can't be here, can she? There's no way...
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Hey, what's with the face, bunny? You've got her all locked up in...
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Damn it, {@nickname}... damn you and damn that Kal'tsit!
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Congratulations, {@nickname}, you're now second on my list of people to bomb.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: W, there's a lot of intel that we haven't shared. We need to get out of here...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Get out? Easy for you to say.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Be glad it's not Talulah here. I don't smell the arrogant stench of Draco fire. But...
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Surround the place!
attributes.name: Sarkaz Mercenary

attributes.content: Theta, Iota, block the path on the other side!
attributes.name: Sarkaz Mercenary

attributes.content: They got so many men in so little time?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Oh no! Doctor, Lady Heidi and the others are still inside!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Sorry, Amiya...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Save that for when we get out.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Very well.
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: Doctor, let me... W? Why are you grabbing me like that?
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Save your strength, bunny. Look at the gang you've got here. Artificer, wounded, garbage... who can fight?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Y-You're right, but we'll do our best...
attributes.name: Feist

attributes.content: W-We won't be a burden.
attributes.name: Rockrock

attributes.content: Save your strength for running. You'll wanna be fast.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Sigh... I didn't want to say this. It's really not my style.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: But I need Heidi alive. There's something I need to ask the old woman.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Go. Take your people, and pick up your trash.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: W!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Good luck. We'll be waiting.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: You're still here? Need me to blow you up?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Finally. Some peace.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: She talks like we're actually friends.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: As for you...
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Wanna keep blasting? At this rate, there won't be much left to bomb.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: What's this? A rock? Some kind of lame joke?
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Congratulations, you've pissed me off.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: I was hoping to be a little frugal today.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Why don't you come out? I promise I'll leave something of you that's recognizable.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: Well, that was close. Only two bombs away from hitting me.
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: You've grown again, W.
Wait, what—
attributes.name: W

attributes.content: You?!
attributes.name: W
